snippet.title: Fat Rat Pinball - E3 2017 - Gameplay (Beta)
snippet.description:
Play pinball with the Fat Rat and friends. No balls, with the animals are funnier! Fat Rat Pinball is a mobile game, where the traditional pinball game scheme changes a little, becoming more varied and different.
Beta version available at GooglePlay Store: 

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.invent4.FatRatPinball

http://www.invent.com
